Package remodel.expr

Class LiteralExpression

java.lang.Object
remodel.expr.Expression
remodel.expr.LiteralExpression
All Implemented Interfaces:
PriorityCodes, TokenCodes
public class LiteralExpression
extends Expression
implements TokenCodes
LiteralExpression is a kind of Expression denoting a literal value. A LiteralExpression encapsulates a type code and the literal value text. The type code is used to interpret the type of literal object.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Anthony J H Simons
